text:
is auto save enabled?


Auto-save functionality depends on the specific application or software you are using. Many modern applications, such as Google Docs, Microsoft Office 365, and various IDEs (Integrated Development Environments), have auto-save features enabled by default to prevent data loss. However, in some cases, you may need to enable it manually or configure the settings according to your preferences.

If you are referring to a specific application, please provide more details so I can give you a more precise answer.
